===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|speken||to speak|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|specan|specan|to speak|lang=ang}}, alteration of earlier {{term|sprecan|sprecan|to speak|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|sprekanan|to speak, make a sound|lang=en}}, from {{proto|Indo-European|spreg-|to make a sound, utter, speak|lang=en}}. Cognate with Dutch {{term|spreken||to speak|lang=nl}}, German {{term|sprechen||to speak|lang=de}}, Albanian {{term|shpreh||to utter, voice, express|lang=sq}}.

